                <p>
                    Relync is a real estate website inspired by the love and desire to link ordinary persons to available and suitable housing by its location first.  
                    The product is a local initiative aiming at solving the everyday housing problems inherent in making a choice of where to stay or own.
                   Property listings are shown by pins at their exact locations on a map of Metropolitan Kampala,each referenced with a brief description. Full descriptions included with a floor plan and a video tour can then be accessed on the detail pages in order to make a sound and informed decision on whether to approach the listing contact or not.
                    It is a first, among others by <strong>
                        Pesh&Dean (U)
                    </strong> with an objective to incorporate tech  to solve the growing need for real estate and housing among the growing middle class population.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The company is well structured with highly qualified and motivated personnel who actively engage in the Ugandan real estate market both as practicing professionals and active market players.
                    Relync has chosen to plug the gap created by the deficit in the housing sector as a result of population growth which makes it more difficult to not only secure housing but also get housing that suits one’s specific tastes and preference. Relync works tirelessly and coherently exploiting the latest technology and innovation to break this barrier providing a diverse pool of housing possibilities at a click of a button.
                </p>

